Attribute.value: The cryptor in this campaign uses several obfuscation techniques that makes it difficult to dissect, and could pose a challenge for security analysts not familiar with Visual Basic 6. Our analysis provides insight into the adversaries' tactics and how the crypter works in detail. These types of attacks are a return to form for classic virus campaigns — video game players are no strangers to trying to avoid malicious downloads while trying to change the game they're playing.
